.v3_demo-hero-testimonials {
  width: 100%;
  max-width: 42rem;
  margin: 4rem auto 0 auto;
}

.v3_demo-flows .swiper-slide {
  text-align: center;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  align-items: center;
}

.v3_demo-hero-testimonials-wrapper {
  width: 120%;
  transform: translateX(-10%);
  padding: 0 12%;
  position: relative;
  z-index: -2;
  mask-image: linear-gradient(to right, transparent 0%, black 15%, black 85%, transparent 100%);
}

.v3_demo-hero-testimonials-pagination {
  display: flex;
  grid-column-gap: 0.5rem;
}

.v3_demo-hero-testimonials-pagination span.swiper-pagination-bullet {
  width: 14px;
  height: 14px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  border: 1px solid rgba(28, 25, 23, 0.8);
  background: transparent;
  margin: 0 !important;
  padding: 0 !important;
}

.v3_demo-hero-testimonials-pagination span.swiper-pagination-bullet.swiper-pagination-bullet-active {
  background: var(--v3-colors--v3-orange-700);
  border-color: var(--v3-colors--v3-orange-700);
}

/* Made pagination left aligned on desktop for Get Started page's Demo Hero testimonials */
@media screen and (min-width: 992px) {
  .v3_demo-hero-content .v3_demo-hero-testimonials-pagination {
    justify-content: flex-start;
  }
}


/* >> Mobile styles */

@media screen and (max-width: 991px) {

  .v3_demo-hero-testimonials {
  	margin: 2rem auto 0 auto;
  }

  .v3_demo-flows .v3_demo-hero-testimonials {
    margin: 4rem auto 0 auto;
  }

}

@media screen and (max-width: 767px) {

  .v3_demo-hero-testimonials-pagination span.swiper-pagination-bullet {
 	 	width: 12px;
  	height: 12px;			
  }

}

We had many issues with TaxJar, including incorrect tax filings that resulted in an overpayment of $5,700 and non-existent customer support. Numeral provided complete onboarding, prompt customer service, and rapid feature additions based on customer input.Kevin Chanthasiriphan,Founder, immiI was spending way too many hours every month on sales tax. Numeral has made it easy to identify and know the tax laws. And then, on your behalf, registering and managing everything takes the worry off my plate.Jesse Hiss,Founder, Fresh SendsIt's set it and forget it. At the end of the day, I'd much rather spend time growing our business than worrying about sales tax. We love Numeral. I don't know how you squeeze a number out of it, but I'd give working with them a 10 out of 10.Adrian Zhang,Co-founder, The WooblesAs a founder, sales tax for my SaaS business was the last thing I wanted to think about. Numeral made it dead simple for Archive to stay compliant across multiple jurisdictions. Plus, their developer experience is thoughtful and built with craft.Paul Benigeri,CEO, ArchiveNumeral tailors its solution to each client’s needs. Everything is customized. And I loved that I could talk to sales tax experts. Numeral guarantees no compliance mistakes will happen. Nobody else was willing to make that promise.Jason Wong,Founder, Doe LashesSales tax compliance is a consistent frustration for my Series A & B SaaS clients. As a busy CFO, I want to spend my energy on strategic work, not compliance. With Numeral, I can delegate away the minutia of state tax compliance.Hari Seshadri,CEO, Fractional4.9 on G2Type of Business

.v3_hero-demo-form {
  background: #F7F2EB;
  border: 1px solid #E3D9CB;
  border-radius: 0.75rem;
  padding: 2.5rem;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  grid-row-gap: 2rem;
  max-width: 32.75rem;
}


.v3_hero-demo-form fieldset {
  max-width: none;
}

.v3_hero-demo-form fieldset.form-columns-2 {
  display: flex;
  grid-column-gap: 0.75rem;
}

.v3_hero-demo-form fieldset:has([type="hidden"]) {
  display: none;
}

.v3_hero-demo-form .hs-form-field {
  position: relative;
}

.v3_hero-demo-form fieldset.form-columns-2 .hs-form-field {
  width: 100%;
  float: none;
  position: relative;
}

.v3_hero-demo-form label {
  border: none;
  color: var(--v3-colors--v3-gray-warm-900);
  font-family: var(--v3-fonts--twk-continental);
  font-size: 0.875rem;
  font-style: normal;
  font-weight: 400;
  line-height: 140%;
  letter-spacing: 0.28px;
  padding: 0;
  margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  background: transparent;
}

.v3_hero-demo-form fieldset .hs-input {
  width: 100% !important;
}

.v3_hero-demo-form fieldset .input {
  margin: 0 !important;
}

.v3_hero-demo-form input  {
  width: 100%;
  height: 3rem;
  padding: 1rem 1.5rem;
  border-radius: 0.5rem;
  border: 1px solid #E3D9CB;
  background: var(--white);
  color: var(--v3-colors--v3-gray-warm-900);
  font-family: var(--v3-fonts--twk-continental);
  font-size: 1rem;
  font-style: normal;
  font-weight: 400;
  line-height: 140%;
}

.v3_hero-demo-form input::placeholder {
  color: rgba(28, 25, 23, 0.40);
}

.v3_hero-demo-form input:focus-visible {
  outline: none;
}

.v3_hero-demo-form select  {
  width: 100%;
  height: 3rem;
  padding: 0 1.5rem;
  border-radius: 0.375rem;
  border: 1px solid #E3D9CB;
  background: var(--white);
  color: var(--v3-colors--v3-gray-warm-900);
  font-family: var(--v3-fonts--twk-continental);
  font-size: 1rem;
  font-style: normal;
  font-weight: 400;
  line-height: 140%;
  letter-spacing: 0.32px;
  appearance: none;
	-moz-appearance: none;
  -webkit-appearance: none;
  background-image: url('https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/63fe7042804e3d54e81443a6/67aa2149f76b53229046f5c6_chevron-down.svg');
  background-repeat: no-repeat;
  background-position: right 1.5rem center;
  cursor: pointer;
}

.v3_hero-demo-form select.is-placeholder {
	color: rgba(28, 25, 23, 0.40);
}

.v3_hero-demo-form select:focus-visible {
  outline: none;
}

.v3_hero-demo-form option {
  color: var(--v3-colors--v3-gray-warm-900);
}


.v3_hero-demo-form input[type="submit"] {
  white-space: nowrap !important;
  border-radius: .5rem;
  border: none !important;
  justify-content: center;
  align-items: center;
  height: 3rem;
  padding: 0 1.25rem;
  text-decoration: none;
  display: flex;
  background: var(--v3-colors--v3-orange-700);
  box-shadow: 0 1px 3px #0a0d121a,0 1px 2px -1px #0a0d121a;
  font-family: var(--v3-fonts--twk-continental);
  color: var(--v3-colors--v3-gray-iron-100);
  white-space: nowrap;
  font-size: 1rem;
  font-weight: 500;
  line-height: 150%;
  text-decoration: none;
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: all 0.2s ease;
}

.v3_hero-demo-form input[type="submit"]:hover {
	background: var(--v3-colors--v3-orange-800);
}

.v3_hero-demo-form .legal-consent-container {
  color: var(--v3-colors--v3-gray-warm-900);
  text-align: center;
  font-family: var(--v3-fonts--twk-continental);
  font-size: 0.875rem;
  font-style: normal;
  font-weight: 400;
  line-height: 140%;
  letter-spacing: 0.24px;
  opacity: 0.5;
}

.v3_hero-demo-form fieldset:has(.legal-consent-container) {
  order: 1;
  margin-top: -0.75rem;
  display: none;
}

ul.hs-error-msgs {
  position: absolute;
  top: 110%;
  width: 100%;
  background: #5c514f;
  border-radius: 0.375rem;
  padding: 0.75rem;
  margin: 0;
  opacity: 0.85;
  list-style: none;
  z-index: 100;
  box-shadow: 0.25rem 0.25rem 1rem rgba(0,0,0,0.35);
}

/* Hide the entire error message container when it contains email suggestions */
ul.hs-error-msgs:has(li label a) {
  display: none !important;
}

label.hs-error-msg {
  color: #fff;
  font-size: 0.75rem;
  font-weight: 400;
  margin: 0;
}

label span.hs-form-required {
  display: none;
}

input[readonly] {
  color: rgba(28, 25, 23, 0.20);
  background: #F4F4F3;
}

@media screen and (max-width: 991px) {

  .v3_hero-demo-form {
    padding: 1.75rem 1.5rem;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .v3_demo-flow-wrapper .v3_hero-demo-form {
    padding: 0 !important;
  }

}

@media screen and (max-width: 767px) {

  .v3_hero-demo-form fieldset.form-columns-2 {
    flex-direction: column;
    grid-row-gap: 2rem;
  }


}







/* >> Styles for Global countries select */

.hs-countries_operating_in .hs-countries_operating_in-trigger {
  border: 1px solid var(--v3-colors--v3-border-color); 
  background-color: var(--v3-colors--v3-gray-warm-25);
  border-radius: .5rem;
  display: flex;
  grid-column-gap: 1rem;
  justify-content: space-between;
  align-items: center;
  width: 100%;
  height: 3rem;
  padding: 0 1.5rem;
  color: rgba(28, 25, 23, 0.40);
  font-family: var(--v3-fonts--twk-continental);
  font-size: 1rem;
  font-style: normal;
  font-weight: 400;
  line-height: 140%;
  letter-spacing: 0.32px;
  cursor: pointer;
  /*
  background-image: url('https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/63fe7042804e3d54e81443a6/67aa2149f76b53229046f5c6_chevron-down.svg');
  background-repeat: no-repeat;
  background-position: right 1.5rem center;
  */
  margin: 0 !important;
  position: relative;
}

.hs-countries_operating_in .hs-countries_operating_in-trigger:after {
  content: "";
  position: absolute;
  right: 1.5rem;
  top: 1rem;
  width: 14px;
  height: 14px;
  background: url('https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/63fe7042804e3d54e81443a6/67aa2149f76b53229046f5c6_chevron-down.svg');
  background-repeat: no-repeat;
  background-size: 14px 14px;
  transition: all 0.2s ease;
}

.hs-countries_operating_in-trigger.expanded:after {
  transform: rotateZ(-180deg);
}

.hs_countries_operating_in-label-text {
  white-space: nowrap;
  overflow: hidden;
  text-overflow: ellipsis;
  max-width: 40ch;
}

.hs-countries_operating_in .input {
  padding-top: 0.5rem;
}

.hs-countries_operating_in ul {
  list-style: none;
  position: absolute;
  top: 100%;
  left: 0;
  z-index: 500;
  border: 1px solid var(--v3-colors--v3-border-color);
  border-radius: .5rem;
  background: var(--v3-colors--v3-gray-warm-25);
  padding: 1rem;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  grid-row-gap: 1rem;
  width: 100%;
  max-height: 0rem;
  overflow-y: auto;
  opacity: 0;
  transition: 0.5s ease;
  margin: 0 !important;
}

/* Expand on hover disabled */
/*
.hs-countries_operating_in:hover ul {
  max-height: 20rem;
  opacity: 1;
  box-shadow: 0px 1px 3px 0px rgba(10, 13, 18, 0.10), 0px 1px 2px -1px rgba(10, 13, 18, 0.10);
}
*/

.hs-countries_operating_in ul.expanded {
  max-height: 20rem;
  opacity: 1;
  box-shadow: 0px 1px 3px 0px rgba(10, 13, 18, 0.10), 0px 1px 2px -1px rgba(10, 13, 18, 0.10);
}

.hs-countries_operating_in .hs-form-checkbox label {
  grid-column-gap: 1rem;
  border: none;
  background-color: var(--v3-colors--v3-gray-warm-25);
  display: flex;
  justify-content: flex-start;
  align-items: center;
  flex-shrink: 0;
  height: 2.375rem;
  padding: 0 1rem 0 3rem;
  position: relative;
  transition: all 0.2s ease;
  cursor: pointer;
}

.hs-countries_operating_in .hs-form-checkbox label:before {
  content: "";
  width: 0.75rem;
  height: 0.75rem;
  position: absolute;
  top: 1.7rem;
  left: 2rem;
  border: 2px solid #E3D9CB;
  border-radius: 4px;
  top: 0.675rem;
  left: 1rem;
  transition: all 0.2s ease;
}


.hs-countries_operating_in .hs-form-checkbox label:has(input[type="checkbox"]:checked):before {
  background: var(--v3-colors--v3-orange-800);
  border-color: var(--v3-colors--v3-orange-800);
  transition: all 0.2s ease;
}

.hs-countries_operating_in .hs-form-checkbox label:has(input[type="checkbox"]:checked):after {
  content: "\2713";
  position: absolute;
  top: 0.9rem;
  left: 1.15rem;
  width: 0.775rem;
  height: 0.775rem;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  font-size: 0.75rem;
  color: #ffffff;
  background: var(--v3-colors--v3-orange-800);
  transition: all 0.2s ease;
}

.hs-countries_operating_in input {
  display: none;
}

.hs-countries_operating_in .hs-form-checkbox label span {
  color: var(--v3-colors--v3-gray-warm-900);
  padding: 0;
  font-family: TWK Continental,Tahoma,sans-serif;
  font-size: 1rem;
  font-weight: 400;
  line-height: normal;
  text-rendering: auto;
}


/* > Country Search */

.hs-countries_operating_in-trigger-country-search {
  position: relative;
  z-index: 500;
  display: none !important;
  border: 0 !important;
  background: transparent !important;
  padding: 0 !important;
  letter-spacing: 0.32px;
}

.hs-countries_operating_in-trigger.expanded .hs-countries_operating_in-trigger-country-search {
  display: block !important;
}

.hs-countries_operating_in-trigger.expanded .hs_countries_operating_in-label-text {
  display: none !important;
}



/* < Country Search */

@media screen and (max-width: 478px) {

  .hs_countries_operating_in-label-text {
    max-width: 25ch;
  }

}

/* << Styles for Global countries select */





